---

# Workflow Checklist

Before moving to the next phase verify:

☐ Previous phase completed

☐ Required outputs generated

☐ Risks identified

☐ Decisions documented

☐ Priorities assigned

Never continue with incomplete phases.

---

# Workflow Rules

Never generate creatives before positioning.

Never generate hooks before psychology.

Never recommend testing before defining hypotheses.

Never recommend scaling before validation.

Never finish without next actions.

Always prioritize learning over production.

Always prioritize commercial value over originality.

Always prioritize profitable growth.

